  "1772830": {
    "name": "Rusted Moss",
    "steam_appid": 1772830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/5ea4a82ee556c2c82eb0b85635a500d5.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=122 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/a82b0f1a470af4514d1f33c739440a1b.poster.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/a82b0f1a470af4514d1f33c739440a1b.webm?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/a82b0f1a470af4514d1f33c739440a1b.mp4?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一款带有物理引擎吊绳的类银河城动作游戏</h2><br><br>在这款类银河城动作游戏中，武器和吊绳都可以360°无死角地发射。颇具自由度的操控性让你可以灵活掌控角色的行动，给你带来丝滑的游戏体验。用颇具创意的方式灵巧地穿越危险地形，再用精准的射击来射爆女巫和机甲吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/a8e2d6dfffadccf12d3b72cdeeced4dc.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=122 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/4feb2845b6e4ce5451b4630c92646a57.poster.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/4feb2845b6e4ce5451b4630c92646a57.webm?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/4feb2845b6e4ce5451b4630c92646a57.mp4?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>吊绳的操作非常困难，但相应的，灵活掌握它也就变得颇具意义。这款基于物理引擎的吊绳有着橡皮筋一样的伸缩性，可以借助动作的惯性来帮助你的角色前进。在这片被遗忘的废墟中，前进的道路绝不仅有一条。勾住青苔丛生的墙壁和屋顶，跨越险要的地形吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/bb19bcc034c2b8a1313f4c46aa27d263.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=122 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/2b53d882aa9f3ed5870ccaa016b52c11.poster.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/2b53d882aa9f3ed5870ccaa016b52c11.webm?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/2b53d882aa9f3ed5870ccaa016b52c11.mp4?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>8方向式移动已经过时啦。作为一款双摇杆式射击游戏，《Rusted Moss》强调快速的反应力和精准的射击。你可以先在近距离之下用散弹枪爆射，然后用吊绳拉开距离，在远处用狙击枪精准地来个收尾。灵活切换武器，找出最适合你的游戏风格以及当前状况的攻击手段吧。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/68dbb49d31835b34814ccefb555806e2.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=122 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/33bd007e6d9b05953ceeea4083893e8a.poster.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/33bd007e6d9b05953ceeea4083893e8a.webm?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/33bd007e6d9b05953ceeea4083893e8a.mp4?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>现在就是让你秀枪法和吊绳技巧的时候了！不论是强大的女巫还是比魔物更加可怕的机甲，每一位BOSS都将为你带来独特的困难挑战。躲开利刃、逃离能量场、快速清扫袭来的变异蜘蛛、攻克强大的BOSS吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创意工坊和地图编辑器！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/788a0b1f274116647f3ff6a6c76b3383.poster.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/788a0b1f274116647f3ff6a6c76b3383.webm?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/788a0b1f274116647f3ff6a6c76b3383.mp4?t=1756369522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用各式各样的地形砖块和机关来制作独一无二的原创关卡，探索银河恶魔城与物理吊绳相结合后的无限可能。此外，您也可以将自己创作的关卡上传至Steam创意工坊，又或者下载其他玩家制作的关卡来游玩体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772830/extras/7d83825213a2902978ec4d12550b2fc1.avif?t=1756369522\" width=600 height=122 /></span><br><br>穿越一片有着淡淡忧伤气氛的废墟，见证残存的人类和他们那锈迹斑斑的机甲的末路…人类正处于灭绝的边缘，很快就会被精灵所取代。为了生存下去，人类便用偷来的精灵魔法创造了他们的女巫。<br><br>可这并不是结束。人类遭到了欺骗。他们本以为是同伴的人实际上却并非如此。精灵偷走了一个人类的婴儿，并用了其它的“东西”取而代之…<br><br>被一无所知的双亲养育成人的主角，就是这个被替换的孩子。如今她将和神秘的黑影帕克一起踏上旅途，将这个世界归还给精灵，结束人类的时代。<br><br>人类和精灵，你站哪一边呢？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过20种独特的能力可供收集。<br></li><li>灵活的通关策略和游戏风格。<br></li><li>超过6位极具挑战性的BOSS。<br></li><li>8种颇具特色的武器可供收集。<br></li><li>拥有多结局的故事剧情。<br></li><li>邂逅在这个世界上飘零的人和精灵，了解他们的故事。<br></li><li>探索化为废墟的神社和计算机站，解开古老的秘密和不为人知的过往<br></li><li>美丽且带有一丝丝伤感的像素艺术。融汇了复古氛围和现代审美，令人不禁情寄其中的像素绘图和动画，使《Rusted Moss》的世界变得优美而又生动。</li></ul>",
